  "detailed_description": "Madville+ is a rogue-lite / arena shooter with ridiculous upgrades. <br><br>Upgrade your character with cards and combine different decks to boost their effects!<br><br>Game is designed to have short play sessions (30-40 min) and replayability. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1934540/extras/840ecbe1893e38216e6195613ba2a5e4.poster.avif?t=1726948542\" width=550 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1934540/extras/840ecbe1893e38216e6195613ba2a5e4.webm?t=1726948542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1934540/extras/840ecbe1893e38216e6195613ba2a5e4.mp4?t=1726948542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>7 unique classes with different abilites:<br>  --->  Bouncer, Carpenter, Scientist, Farmer, Survivalist, Gambler, Indie Game Developer!<br>- Lots of guns<br>- Lots of add-ons for your guns<br>- Lots of passive effects<br>- Lots of aliens<br>- Lots of dice and random effects<br>- Ridiculous challenges<br><br>Game includes an auto-aim&shoot toggle, so you can play it like a straight twin-stick shooter or a more modern/casual arena survival game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1934540/extras/f57665d797ade785117c4411509b95a2.poster.avif?t=1726948542\" width=506 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1934540/extras/f57665d797ade785117c4411509b95a2.webm?t=1726948542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1934540/extras/f57665d797ade785117c4411509b95a2.mp4?t=1726948542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Madville+ is a rogue-lite / arena shooter with ridiculous upgrades. <br><br>Upgrade your character with cards and combine different decks to boost their effects!<br><br>Game is designed to have short play sessions (30-40 min) and replayability. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1934540/extras/840ecbe1893e38216e6195613ba2a5e4.poster.avif?t=1726948542\" width=550 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1934540/extras/840ecbe1893e38216e6195613ba2a5e4.webm?t=1726948542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1934540/extras/840ecbe1893e38216e6195613ba2a5e4.mp4?t=1726948542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>7 unique classes with different abilites:<br>  --->  Bouncer, Carpenter, Scientist, Farmer, Survivalist, Gambler, Indie Game Developer!<br>- Lots of guns<br>- Lots of add-ons for your guns<br>- Lots of passive effects<br>- Lots of aliens<br>- Lots of dice and random effects<br>- Ridiculous challenges<br><br>Game includes an auto-aim&shoot toggle, so you can play it like a straight twin-stick shooter or a more modern/casual arena survival game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1934540/extras/f57665d797ade785117c4411509b95a2.poster.avif?t=1726948542\" width=506 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1934540/extras/f57665d797ade785117c4411509b95a2.webm?t=1726948542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1934540/extras/f57665d797ade785117c4411509b95a2.mp4?t=1726948542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
